FBIS3-13425 "drnes049_l_94020" FBIS-NES-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 ISRAEL IDF Will Not Change Firing Rules on Settlers TA1103204594 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in Hebrew 1800 GMT 11 Mar 94 TA1103204594 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] will not revise the rules governing shooting at Jewish settlers. A senior defense source has told our military correspondent Roni Daniyel that the orders banning gunfire on Jews does not apply to cases such as the Hebron massacre, contrary to the testimony of the Hebron Border Police company commander at the Shamgar Commission session.
